r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=74ed45fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"90140856f13b9cf2abeb42a6b063b15fda1ce120","tid":1704563,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"逼自己成長啦"},{"pid":"ab360581fb0d15fb941897da92b4df96e54adc58","tid":1704563,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55d96dd5ecb1da8a0a79a1a935f5d38cdb247750","tid":1704563,"uid":161743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得每日part 唔同同事先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗故意social 唔好嘅對一日就bye bye<br />\n煩少好多人際關係 <br />\n出面嘅工唔好嘅同事要日日對喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca3c76d4d1662fbbe1f12b307c661d2f0f31e6b","tid":1704563,"uid":94465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55d96dd5ecb1da8a0a79a1a935f5d38cdb247750","tid":1704563,"uid":161743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得每日part 唔同同事先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗故意social 唔好嘅對一日就bye bye<br />\n煩少好多人際關係 <br />\n出面嘅工唔好嘅同事要日日對喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"我都係咁話<br />\n又可以見多啲唔同既人"},{"pid":"b4beafb76686c41185b112e87499e72ab57bcc5a","tid":1704563,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b176153dc82818e6017ff1fa24b32cb5ec44dbb","tid":1704563,"uid":88154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79d451f9fca726ef